data.title: Career Center
data.text:
Start Your Journey With Dallas ISD! Apply to Our Dallas ISD 2024-2025 Teacher Application!

If you would like to work in a school district that is innovative, diverse, and focused on your professional growth, then consider applying to teach at Dallas Independent School District. Dallas ISD is the 2nd largest school district in Texas, serving over 135,000+ students. Dallas ISD prides itself in outperforming the state and continues to be on the cutting edge of educational opportunities. Join our community of educators and administrators who bring diverse skills and experience as we strive to become the premier urban school district in the country.

Dallas ISD Upcoming Events

Sign up for our Dallas ISD job fairs and events at www.DallasISD.org/hcmjobfair!

Apply to our Dallas ISD 2024-2025 Teacher Application today!

Become a Substitute Today
